        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>shaping and guiding tools [300162806], shaping and guiding equipment [300024808], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of various tools, usually long bars or strips of wood or metal, having straight and true edges and used for drawing or cutting accurate straight lines or for testing levelness or the evenness of surfaces. For, usually shorter, instruments used primarily as guides for drawing lines, straight or curved, use "rulers (measuring tools)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Diverse gereedschappen, meestal lange staven of repen van hout of metaal, die zuiver rechte kanten hebben en worden gebruikt om nauwkeurige rechte lijnen te tekenen of te snijden, of om de vlakheid of gelijkmatigheid van oppervlakken te controleren. Gebruik 'linialen (geleidingsgereedschap)' voor meestal kortere voorwerpen die voornamelijk worden gebruikt als geleiders om rechte of gebogen lijnen te tekenen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052374/Polytechnisch woordenboek En-Ne (1991)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>各種不同的工具，通常為木製或金屬製的長棒或長條，具有筆直且精準的邊緣，用以繪製或切割精確的直線，或檢驗平面的水平度或平坦度。若指長度通常較短的儀器，主要用於引導畫線之用（直線或曲線不拘），則稱「尺(測量儀器)」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
